                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for rapidly synthesizing 1, 3-diaminothiourea through one-pot method",
                    "一锅法快速合成1,3-二氨基硫脲的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to a method for rapidly synthesizing 1, 3-diaminothiourea by a one-pot process, which comprises the following steps: arranging a thermometer, a dropping funnel and a piston containing a conduit on a four-neck flask, adding a certain amount of ammonia water solution with the mass fraction of 10%, a certain amount of hydrogen peroxide solution with the mass fraction of 5% and a certain amount of mercaptoethanol into the four-neck flask, adding carbon disulfide into the dropping funnel, and reacting for 2-4 hours at the temperature of 50-60 DEG C; placing the four-neck flask in an ultrasonic reactor, and setting the ultrasonic frequency to be 60-65kHZ, the power to be 400W and the heating temperature to be 40 DEG C; when the temperature of the material in the flask is 40 DEG C, starting to dropwise add carbon disulfide, and starting an ultrasonic-assisted reaction at the same time; after the reaction is finished, naturally cooling to room temperature, and filtering a product to obtain a crude product 1, 3-diaminothiourea; and purifying and drying to obtain the finished product 1, 3-diaminothiourea. According to the method, the ultrasonic radiation is adopted to assist the reaction, so that the 1, 3-diaminothiourea can be quickly and efficiently synthesized by a one-pot method, and the defects of long synthesis time, high reaction temperature, harsh conditions, low yield and the like in the prior art are overcome."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及一种一锅法快速合成1,3‑二氨基硫脲的方法，在一四口烧瓶上装备温度计、滴液漏斗及含有导管的活塞，在四口烧瓶中加入一定量质量分数为10％的氨水溶液、质量分数为5％的过氧化氢溶液及巯基乙醇，滴液漏斗中加入二硫化碳，四口烧瓶置于超声波反应器中，设定超声波频率为60‑65kHZ，功率为400W，加热温度为40℃；当烧瓶内物料温度为40℃时，开始滴加二硫化碳，同时开启超声波辅助反应；反应结束后，自然冷却至室温，产物过滤得到粗品1,3‑二氨基硫脲；纯化并烘干后得到成品1,3‑二氨基硫脲。本发明采用超声波辐射辅助反应，可以一锅法快速高效地合成1,3‑二氨基硫脲，解决了现有技术合成时间长，反应温度高，条件苛刻，产率不高等缺陷。"
                }
            ]
